Upstream reference
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
This crate reimplements the algorithms of ROOT Minuit2:

    Minuit2 is part of ROOT (https://root.cern).
    Copyright (c) 2005 LCG ROOT Math team, CERN/PH-SFT
    Authors: M. Winkler, F. James, L. Moneta, A. Zsenei  (2003-2005)
